From af8c859dbe1614de46794c4b3f40fb75486586f6 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Daniel van Vugt <daniel.van.vugt@canonical.com>
Date: Wed, 23 Jun 2021 18:04:16 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 6/6] onscreen/native: Remove an assertion that we're not
 triple buffering

Because we are now occasionally triple buffering so the warning is no
